enhanced_by.reason: generateInvalid relies on generateValid to create a valid base ID number before modifying it to be invalid.
Both methods involve generating random numbers within a specified range.
The invalid ID number generated by generateInvalid can be compared against the valid ID number generated by generateValid to ensure the invalidation process is correctly applied.
Both methods involve manipulating and validating ID numbers, which can inform the construction of assertions to verify the correctness of the invalidation process.
